00:00:06.273 --> 00:00:08.275 position:33% line:83% align:start
Hey, Brother,
the time is now.

00:00:08.308 --> 00:00:09.309 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:00:09.677 --> 00:00:10.678 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:00:12.647 --> 00:00:14.314 position:27% line:89% align:start
Here I go, Masao.

00:00:15.382 --> 00:00:15.750 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:00:16.818 --> 00:00:19.219 position:35% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>What?</i>
 <i>What's happening?</i>

00:00:19.253 --> 00:00:20.487 position:30% line:83% align:start
-This is our...
-This is our...

00:00:20.522 --> 00:00:23.290 position:16% line:83% align:start
-new special technique...
-new special technique...

00:00:23.323 --> 00:00:24.726 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Skylab...
-Skylab...

00:00:24.759 --> 00:00:27.695 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Hurricane!
-Hurricane!

00:00:27.729 --> 00:00:29.363 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[gasps]
-[ann] <i>Incredible!</i>

00:00:29.396 --> 00:00:32.099 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>One of the twins has been</i>
 <i>thrusted like a projectile</i>

00:00:32.132 --> 00:00:33.200 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>towards the sky</i>

00:00:33.233 --> 00:00:36.303 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>and now he's...</i>
 <i>he's...he's flying!</i>

00:00:36.336 --> 00:00:38.338 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>What a beautiful</i>
 <i>thing to see!</i>

00:00:39.239 --> 00:00:42.042 position:41% line:83% align:start
[yell]
[grunt]

00:00:42.075 --> 00:00:43.277 position:38% line:89% align:start
[snicker]

00:00:43.778 --> 00:00:45.713 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yell]

00:00:45.747 --> 00:00:47.882 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[Mamoru] Morisaki!
-[grunt]

00:00:47.916 --> 00:00:48.983 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>Goal!</i>

00:00:49.017 --> 00:00:50.450 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>What a goal!</i>

00:00:50.484 --> 00:00:53.821 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>The Tachibana Twins have</i>
 <i>scored with an amazing shot.</i>

00:00:53.855 --> 00:00:55.757 position:35% line:83% align:start
Incredible.
That can't be!

00:02:35.222 --> 00:02:36.591 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[narr] <i>Episode 38:</i>
-[cheering]

00:02:36.624 --> 00:02:39.927 position:38% line:83% align:start
 <i>Assault!</i>
 <i>Tachibana Brothers.</i>

00:02:39.961 --> 00:02:41.129 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Team Hanawa</i>
 <i>closes the gap</i>

00:02:41.161 --> 00:02:42.030 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>and now they're just</i>

00:02:42.063 --> 00:02:43.230 position:30% line:83% align:start
- <i>one goal away</i>
-[laughs]

00:02:43.263 --> 00:02:44.732 position:19% line:83% align:start
- <i>from tying the match.</i>
-Did you see that?

00:02:44.766 --> 00:02:46.734 position:16% line:83% align:start
What did you think about
our Skylab Hurricane?

00:02:46.768 --> 00:02:49.003 position:24% line:83% align:start
We're the only ones
capable of performing

00:02:49.037 --> 00:02:50.638 position:27% line:83% align:start
that amazing shot
in the air.

00:02:50.672 --> 00:02:52.540 position:30% line:83% align:start
I never thought
the twin's game

00:02:52.573 --> 00:02:54.307 position:24% line:83% align:start
would ever improve
to that level.

00:02:54.341 --> 00:02:56.476 position:13% line:83% align:start
Well, you had better start
believing it.

00:02:56.511 --> 00:02:59.647 position:13% line:83% align:start
We saw how Masao and Kazuo
trained day and night...

00:02:59.681 --> 00:03:02.449 position:21% line:83% align:start
to be able to perfect
that complicated shot.

00:03:06.721 --> 00:03:07.922 position:41% line:89% align:start
[pants]

00:03:07.955 --> 00:03:09.891 position:13% line:89% align:start
I think we did it, Brother.

00:03:09.924 --> 00:03:11.859 position:30% line:83% align:start
It's not enough
to do it once.

00:03:11.893 --> 00:03:13.828 position:10% line:89% align:start
We must perfect it, Brother.

00:03:13.861 --> 00:03:15.697 position:16% line:89% align:start
But my legs really hurt.

00:03:15.730 --> 00:03:16.964 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:03:16.998 --> 00:03:18.700 position:16% line:83% align:start
This time, I'll give you
the boost.

00:03:18.733 --> 00:03:19.901 position:21% line:89% align:start
Come on, get up now.

00:03:20.902 --> 00:03:22.302 position:27% line:89% align:start
Okay, all right.

00:03:22.335 --> 00:03:23.805 position:19% line:83% align:start
Guys, you don't have to
rush it.

00:03:23.838 --> 00:03:26.007 position:21% line:83% align:start
You know you can keep
training tomorrow.

00:03:26.040 --> 00:03:26.974 position:47% line:83% align:start
No.
We can't do that.

00:03:27.008 --> 00:03:28.442 position:30% line:83% align:start
We can't waste
a single second

00:03:28.475 --> 00:03:30.945 position:13% line:83% align:start
until we completely perfect
the Hurricane Shot.

00:03:30.978 --> 00:03:32.212 position:10% line:89% align:start
Yeah, you're right, Brother.

00:03:32.245 --> 00:03:34.982 position:19% line:83% align:start
If not, we won't stand
a chance against Nankatsu.

00:03:35.016 --> 00:03:36.283 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Let's go.
-Yeah.

00:03:37.350 --> 00:03:39.020 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Nobuo] <i>They were training</i>
 <i>day and night</i>

00:03:39.053 --> 00:03:40.054 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>without any rest.</i>

00:03:40.088 --> 00:03:41.556 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:03:41.589 --> 00:03:42.890 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yell]

00:03:42.924 --> 00:03:44.559 position:38% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:03:45.258 --> 00:03:46.761 position:10% line:89% align:start
And thanks to their efforts,

00:03:46.794 --> 00:03:49.030 position:19% line:83% align:start
we now possess the most
dangerous weapon

00:03:49.063 --> 00:03:50.230 position:27% line:83% align:start
that will ensure
our victory.

00:03:50.263 --> 00:03:52.066 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:03:52.100 --> 00:03:54.234 position:41% line:89% align:start
[growl]

00:03:54.702 --> 00:03:55.469 position:41% line:89% align:start
Uhh...

00:03:55.503 --> 00:03:57.605 position:24% line:83% align:start
That new technique
was excellent.

00:03:57.638 --> 00:03:59.707 position:16% line:83% align:start
And it seems like there's
no way to counter it

00:03:59.741 --> 00:04:00.842 position:33% line:89% align:start
and stop it.

00:04:00.875 --> 00:04:03.778 position:13% line:83% align:start
That new technique is going
to be a very big problem.

00:04:03.811 --> 00:04:06.279 position:24% line:83% align:start
No one will be able
to stop that shot.

00:04:06.313 --> 00:04:08.149 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's a foolproof technique.

00:04:08.182 --> 00:04:09.550 position:21% line:89% align:start
Am I right, Captain?

00:04:09.584 --> 00:04:09.751 position:33% line:89% align:start
So it seems.

00:04:10.785 --> 00:04:12.787 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Hikaru] What are you
going to do, Tsubasa?

00:04:14.922 --> 00:04:15.923 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:04:19.060 --> 00:04:20.293 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Hikaru]
 <i>Hyuga...</i>

00:04:21.195 --> 00:04:23.330 position:10% line:89% align:start
So, "Skylab Hurricane", huh?

00:04:25.066 --> 00:04:26.834 position:16% line:83% align:start
Listen, were you able to
capture that?

00:04:26.868 --> 00:04:29.103 position:19% line:83% align:start
Yeah. It's been a while
since I'd seen

00:04:29.137 --> 00:04:30.938 position:19% line:83% align:start
such an incredible shot
live.

00:04:30.972 --> 00:04:32.039 position:13% line:89% align:start
Well, stop me if I'm wrong,

00:04:32.073 --> 00:04:33.306 position:27% line:83% align:start
but if I remember
correctly...

00:04:33.340 --> 00:04:35.275 position:27% line:83% align:start
the Triangle Shot
is performed

00:04:35.308 --> 00:04:37.145 position:21% line:83% align:start
by using a corner of
the goalpost to jump

00:04:37.178 --> 00:04:38.513 position:19% line:89% align:start
and complete the shot.

00:04:39.312 --> 00:04:41.816 position:35% line:83% align:start
That forms
a perfect triangle.

00:04:43.718 --> 00:04:46.187 position:21% line:83% align:start
However, the "Skylab
Hurricane" technique

00:04:46.220 --> 00:04:47.688 position:27% line:83% align:start
allows the person
that's jumping

00:04:47.722 --> 00:04:49.223 position:24% line:83% align:start
to connect directly
with the shot,

00:04:49.257 --> 00:04:51.793 position:21% line:83% align:start
without depending on
the goalpost for impulse.

00:04:51.826 --> 00:04:55.830 position:16% line:83% align:start
Whoever is on the ground
becomes a human trampoline.

00:04:55.863 --> 00:04:57.565 position:16% line:89% align:start
This match is incredible.

00:04:57.598 --> 00:05:00.535 position:33% line:83% align:start
Team Nankatsu
is in serious problems.

00:05:00.568 --> 00:05:02.970 position:21% line:83% align:start
What's you next move
going to be, Tsubasa?

00:05:04.172 --> 00:05:06.274 position:38% line:83% align:start
Nankatsu,
I want you to remain calm.

00:05:06.306 --> 00:05:07.275 position:33% line:89% align:start
Remain calm?

00:05:07.307 --> 00:05:08.743 position:21% line:83% align:start
How do you expect me
to calm down

00:05:08.776 --> 00:05:10.611 position:33% line:83% align:start
after seeing
that incredible shot?

00:05:10.645 --> 00:05:12.445 position:10% line:89% align:start
It's impressive, no doubt...

00:05:12.479 --> 00:05:13.848 position:19% line:89% align:start
but it's not foolproof.

00:05:13.881 --> 00:05:16.349 position:13% line:83% align:start
They depend on an elevated
pass to complete it.

00:05:16.383 --> 00:05:17.118 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Oh!
-Oh!

00:05:17.151 --> 00:05:18.586 position:16% line:89% align:start
Yeah, that's true, guys.

00:05:18.619 --> 00:05:19.821 position:24% line:83% align:start
Well, since that's
the case...

00:05:19.854 --> 00:05:21.421 position:19% line:83% align:start
we should put pressure
on the player

00:05:21.454 --> 00:05:22.623 position:16% line:89% align:start
making the elevated pass

00:05:22.657 --> 00:05:24.258 position:19% line:83% align:start
so he's unable to pass
to the twins.

00:05:24.292 --> 00:05:25.693 position:21% line:89% align:start
Of course, I get it.

00:05:25.726 --> 00:05:27.895 position:16% line:83% align:start
Instead of just defending
their shots...

00:05:27.929 --> 00:05:28.729 position:21% line:89% align:start
we'll keep attacking.

00:05:28.763 --> 00:05:31.032 position:16% line:83% align:start
That way they won't have
that chance.

00:05:31.065 --> 00:05:31.899 position:44% line:89% align:start
Mhm.

00:05:31.933 --> 00:05:32.700 position:27% line:89% align:start
All right, team.

00:05:32.733 --> 00:05:34.035 position:27% line:83% align:start
Now it's our turn
to counterattack.

00:05:34.068 --> 00:05:36.369 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:05:38.172 --> 00:05:40.708 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>You're not going to lose,</i>
 <i>Tsubasa.</i>

00:05:40.741 --> 00:05:43.077 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'm the only one who can</i>
 <i>defeat you.</i>

00:05:43.110 --> 00:05:46.681 position:35% line:89% align:start
[cheering]

00:05:46.714 --> 00:05:50.417 position:19% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Team Myoko tries</i>
 <i>to score the goal of honor.</i>

00:05:50.450 --> 00:05:51.953 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunt]
-[ann] <i>But the goalkeeper,</i>

00:05:51.986 --> 00:05:52.854 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>Ken Wakashimazu,</i>

00:05:52.887 --> 00:05:54.255 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>doesn't let</i>
 <i>anything through.</i>

00:05:54.288 --> 00:05:55.355 position:30% line:89% align:start
That can't be!

00:05:55.388 --> 00:05:56.190 position:27% line:89% align:start
Really nice save,

00:05:56.224 --> 00:05:57.725 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Wakashimazu.
-Ah!

00:05:57.758 --> 00:05:59.126 position:19% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>In the absence of</i>
 <i>Hyuga,</i>

00:05:59.160 --> 00:06:00.328 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>their goalie</i>
 <i>Wakashimazu,</i>

00:06:00.360 --> 00:06:02.362 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>has become the pillar</i>
 <i>of the team.</i>

00:06:02.395 --> 00:06:05.465 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Kitazume]
 <i>We don't need Hyuga to win.</i>

00:06:05.498 --> 00:06:06.734 position:30% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Up until</i>
 <i>this moment,</i>

00:06:06.767 --> 00:06:09.971 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Toho's goalkeeper hasn't</i>
 <i>let one single goal in</i>

00:06:10.004 --> 00:06:11.005 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>during the tournament.</i>

00:06:12.139 --> 00:06:13.440 position:44% line:83% align:start
[Ken]
 <i>Now that I'm the captain,</i>

00:06:13.473 --> 00:06:15.977 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>I can't allow another team</i>
 <i>to score on us.</i>

00:06:16.010 --> 00:06:18.012 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>Our only rival is Nankatsu.</i>

00:06:19.080 --> 00:06:19.914 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Takeshi]
 <i>Hyuga could've been</i>

00:06:19.947 --> 00:06:21.448 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>the best scorer</i>
 <i>in the tournament</i>

00:06:21.481 --> 00:06:23.184 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>for the third time in a row,</i>

00:06:23.217 --> 00:06:25.086 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>but he decided to train</i>
 <i>on his own</i>

00:06:25.119 --> 00:06:28.122 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>so he could improve</i>
 <i>and defeat Nankatsu.</i>

00:06:28.155 --> 00:06:29.323 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:06:29.357 --> 00:06:30.958 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>We won't let...</i>

00:06:30.992 --> 00:06:32.894 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>his sacrifice be in vain.</i>

00:06:34.262 --> 00:06:37.765 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>We must remain undefeated</i>
 <i>until he's back on our team,</i>

00:06:37.798 --> 00:06:39.967 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>and he's our captain</i>
 <i>once again.</i>

00:06:42.103 --> 00:06:44.572 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And Team Hanawa</i>
 <i>recovers the ball.</i>

00:06:44.605 --> 00:06:47.275 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Thanks to the Tachibana</i>
 <i>twins' spectacular goal,</i>

00:06:47.308 --> 00:06:49.644 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>we see the Hanawa</i>
 <i>in a new light.</i>

00:06:49.677 --> 00:06:51.812 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Let's see if they'll</i>
 <i>be able to tie the game</i>

00:06:51.846 --> 00:06:54.882 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>with Nankatsu before</i>
 <i>the first half is up.</i>

00:06:54.916 --> 00:06:55.883 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[pants]
-Nobuo!

00:06:55.917 --> 00:06:58.286 position:33% line:83% align:start
We must even
the score immediately.

00:06:58.319 --> 00:06:59.053 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah!

00:06:59.086 --> 00:07:00.453 position:19% line:89% align:start
Hiroshi, mark him now.

00:07:00.487 --> 00:07:01.789 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yeah, I got him.

00:07:02.256 --> 00:07:04.592 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:07:04.625 --> 00:07:06.260 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Team Nankatsu</i>
 <i>marks their players</i>

00:07:06.294 --> 00:07:07.795 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>and doesn't let</i>
 <i>Team Hanawa through.</i>

00:07:07.828 --> 00:07:10.197 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>They want to prevent</i>
 <i>any passes come what may.</i>

00:07:10.231 --> 00:07:12.266 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:07:12.300 --> 00:07:13.968 position:16% line:89% align:start
Pass the ball, I'm open.

00:07:14.001 --> 00:07:14.969 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:07:16.436 --> 00:07:18.339 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Stop him now!
-Huh?

00:07:18.372 --> 00:07:19.407 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:07:19.439 --> 00:07:20.141 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:07:20.975 --> 00:07:21.876 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>Aimoto spins</i>

00:07:21.909 --> 00:07:23.077 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>and manages to escape</i>
 <i>with the ball.</i>

00:07:23.110 --> 00:07:24.011 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Wha--?
-This can't be!

00:07:24.045 --> 00:07:26.213 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Perfect! Let's go!
-Perfect! Let's go!

00:07:26.247 --> 00:07:27.415 position:19% line:89% align:start
You won't get through.

00:07:27.447 --> 00:07:28.616 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Go!
-[gasp]

00:07:28.649 --> 00:07:30.584 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Team Hanawa manages</i>
 <i>to make the pass</i>

00:07:30.618 --> 00:07:32.887 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>and the ball is</i>
 <i>flying high.</i>

00:07:32.920 --> 00:07:34.555 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>The Tachibana Twins</i>
 <i>are getting ready to</i>

00:07:34.588 --> 00:07:37.158 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>perform their technique</i>
 <i>once again.</i>

00:07:37.191 --> 00:07:40.728 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa] <i>No! We weren't</i>
 <i>able to prevent the pass.</i>

00:07:40.761 --> 00:07:42.129 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:07:44.131 --> 00:07:45.366 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>What do I do?</i>

00:07:45.399 --> 00:07:46.901 position:27% line:89% align:start
Here I go, Masao.

00:07:47.902 --> 00:07:50.037 position:19% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And the energetic</i>
 <i>Tachibana Twins</i>

00:07:50.071 --> 00:07:50.905 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>are at it again!</i>

00:07:51.672 --> 00:07:53.207 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>What should I do?</i>

00:07:53.240 --> 00:07:54.208 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:07:55.475 --> 00:07:56.644 position:41% line:89% align:start
I know.

00:07:57.645 --> 00:07:59.213 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunt]
-[ann] <i>Incredible!</i>

00:07:59.246 --> 00:08:01.949 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa uses the goalpost</i>
 <i>to drive himself in the air.</i>

00:08:01.983 --> 00:08:02.950 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa.

00:08:02.984 --> 00:08:05.086 position:16% line:83% align:start
He's going to try to stop
the Skylab Hurricane

00:08:05.119 --> 00:08:06.087 position:35% line:83% align:start
-in midair!
-[gasp]

00:08:06.787 --> 00:08:07.521 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

