 <i>Goal!</i>

00:17:13.133 --> 00:17:15.435 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Hanawa is finally</i>
 <i>able to score the goal</i>

00:17:15.469 --> 00:17:18.006 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>to tie the match</i>
 <i>on minute 37.</i>

00:17:18.038 --> 00:17:18.973 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah!

00:17:19.007 --> 00:17:20.708 position:21% line:83% align:start
That's how you do it,
Hanawa!

00:17:20.742 --> 00:17:22.877 position:13% line:89% align:start
Nice job, Masao and Kazuo!

00:17:22.911 --> 00:17:23.978 position:21% line:89% align:start
